definitions.definition: Made with a somewhat elevated position of some certain part of the tongue, in relation to the palate; midway between the high and the low; said of certain vowel sounds, such as, [e o ɛ ɔ] .

definitions.label_groups: originally African-American Vernacular and Internet slang

secondary_definitions: ( linguistics ) Made with a somewhat elevated position of some certain part of the tongue, in relation to the palate; midway between the high and the low; said of certain vowel sounds, such as, [e o ɛ ɔ] .
( originally African-American Vernacular and Internet slang ) Mediocre ; of middling quality.
( Internet slang , by extension ) Trashy ; low-quality .
